&lt;li&gt;Define the product vision and roadmap in partnership with relevant aiEDU leaders and stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define the problem space, surface constraints, and document current-state pain points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct stakeholder interviews, user testing and other research to guide product development and feature prioritization&lt;/li&gt;
